<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Tørk Hviid did it, as a creepy scientific researcher into a parasitic worm Isaiah caught in a mystical pool caused by a magic meteorite buried in a gl<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Tørk Hviid did it, as a creepy scientific researcher into a parasitic worm Isaiah caught in a mystical pool caused by a magic meteorite buried in a glacier on an island off the west coast of Greenland. But the last sentence of the book pretty much sums it up: "There will be no resolution." Sure, you want Smilla and the mechanic to live happily every after, but that's not likely, either. Make you want to go swim in ice water, eh?<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
