      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/369288.Peter_H_eg">About Peter Høeg</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/369288.Peter_H_eg"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1251023278p3/369288.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/369288.Peter_H_eg">Peter Høeg
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
691
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer8231906336775659147">Peter Høeg was born in Copenhagen, Denmark. Before becoming a writer, he worked variously as a sailor, ballet dancer, and actor. He published his first novel, <em>A History of Danish Dreams</em> (1988), to positive reviews. However, it was <em>Smilla’s Sense of Snow</em> (1992), a million-copy best seller, that earned Høeg immediate and international literary celebrity. His books have been published in more than th</span>
  <span id="freeText8231906336775659147" style="display:none">Peter Høeg was born in Copenhagen, Denmark. Before becoming a writer, he worked variously as a sailor, ballet dancer, and actor. He published his first novel, <em>A History of Danish Dreams</em> (1988), to positive reviews. However, it was <em>Smilla’s Sense of Snow</em> (1992), a million-copy best seller, that earned Høeg immediate and international literary celebrity. His books have been published in more than thirty countries.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8231906336775659147" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

